  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DeiktoLoader.DocumentTransformation
    Implement this interface to define a new transformation.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DeiktoLoader
    This class provides static methods for loading a dictionary with an old format.
    Transform918
    The main upgrade here is a change in the way in which custom traits are loaded.
    Transform919
    The main upgrade here is a change in the way in which P2NotMine_Mine, P2Worthless_Valuable and KnowsMe traits are loaded.
    Transform920  
    Transform921  
    Transform922
    Removes uses of p2Worthless_Valuable by replacing it with a custom prop trait Worthless_Valuable.
    Transform923
    Removes uses of p2NotMine_Mine by replacing it with a custom prop trait NotMine_Mine.
    Transform924
    Process operator change from "ForceFateToReact" to "PermitFateToReact" by converting script tokens.
    Transform925
    Change knowsMe elements.
    Transform930
    Replaces ActorSum and GroupSum with Actor@Sum and GroupAverage with Actor@Average.
    Transform931
    Replaces ActorSum and GroupSum with Actor@Sum and GroupAverage with Actor@Average.
    Transform932
    Replaces Familiarity operators with undefined operators, deletes AdjustFamiliarity emotional reactions and deletes familiarity values from actor traits.
    Transform933
    Replaces Acceptable operators by its group versions.
    Transform934
    Renames parameter labels to remove the last "?" character.
    Transform935
    Renames inclination scripts to desirable, and creates dummy acceptable scripts.
    Transform936
    Renames assumeRoleIf scripts to use the tag "assumeRoleIf".
    Transform937
    Removes the OK verb.
    Transform938
    Replaces old operators NominativePronoun, GenitivePronoun and AccusativePronoun with new versions using a new argument.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    DeiktoLoader.BadVersionException
    A class for exceptions when a given dictionary format version can not be loaded.
